[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]very significantly, the Jacobs report accepted that Conemaster would save at least 30 minutes per road closure for the installation and removal of traffic cones and lamps with the resulting fin
[normal]ancial efficiencies – despite this the industry (and HA) have been unwilling to invest in the new technology. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]iv)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The Jacobs report accepted that Conemaster would significantly improve road worker safety, reduce congestion, and offer savings of around £5.5m 
[normal]per year. It assessed Conemaster as a “high value for money” product with a benefit to cost ratio of 2.06
[normal]*[bold]From the results it can be seen 13,000 hours per year of extra lane availability is achievable across the Strategic Road Network.
