[normal]&#xa0;[bold]3.6
[normal] 
[normal] There is a lack of transparency relating to important matters such as safety. Under-reporting of work-related incidents has existed across the HA Network for many years. Despite this, figures for road worker incidents did 
[normal]not show significant improvement. The Committee might wish to challenge why road worker incidents have escalated to 1747 over the past 12 months. 
[normal](as discussed earlier in item 1.1 above)
